{"tid":2412663,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"車CAM直擊｜灣仔六旬漢攝車罅過馬路捱的士撞　昏迷送院搶救","createTime":"2021-02-18T07:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T07:39:38.000Z","uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"219e6744653f95de6d25c98635ef5a09eb7798c6","tid":2412663,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRQdxa2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRQdxa2.gif&h=0f188467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（18日）早上9時許，灣仔軒尼詩道往中環方向近天樂里，一輛的士撞到一名男子，60歲姓賴的傷者重創倒地，昏迷不醒，由救護車送往醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳事發一刻的車cam片，見到男事主原本於行人路上，突然走到馬路，懷疑欲橫過馬路，他先是揮手示意一輛正在行駛中的巴士停車，然後「攝車罅」跑出馬路，期間事主疑突然跌倒，撞到一輛行駛中的的士，重傷倒地。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署宣佈，因交通意外，軒尼詩道往中環方向近天樂里的部份行車線現已封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車。現時上址交通繁忙。<br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n原車cam片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/191226174561957/posts/1477211209296774/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F191226174561957%2Fposts%2F1477211209296774%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=dfe8239a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/191226174561957/posts/1477211209296774/</a>"},{"pid":"1cc376a61744353e8743f77bb7055544612a498d","tid":2412663,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"係的士捱你撞"},{"pid":"4d65a67d9d1828a218c0ca1e30171d4eddb03f0b","tid":2412663,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"廢老累死人"},{"pid":"c879946a2c31c6d6fe53dbcd0e7e200102d313bf","tid":2412663,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"賽跑冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811af97b26274c6e7642b93351057f23212372b0","tid":2412663,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"又IRONMAN 咁款截停啲車"},{"pid":"8b6aa9f